o ensure their mental wellness.\", \"from\": 2960, \"to\": 3137, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3001, \"end\": 3008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Simpson\", \"score\": 0.9958760009211935, \"rank\": 0.004140997544037932, \"text\": \"Jessica\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Simpson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Simpson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Team USA High-Performance Center\", \"from\": 2963, \"to\": 2999}, {\"ngram\": \"the USOPC senior director\", \"from\": 3018, \"to\": 3043}, {\"ngram\": \"psychological services\", \"from\": 3047, \"to\": 3069}, {\"ngram\": \"U.S. athletes\", \"from\": 3090, \"to\": 3103}, {\"ngram\": \"their mental wellness\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3135}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team USA has developed group and individual therapy programs for athletes, including building a popular sleep program.\", \"from\": 3139, \"to\": 3257, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3139, \"end\": 3147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.7212326095557564e-12, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"group\", \"from\": 3162, \"to\": 3167}, {\"ngram\": \"individual therapy programs\", \"from\": 3172, \"to\": 3199}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 3204, \"to\": 3212}, {\"ngram\": \"a popular sleep program\", \"from\": 3233, \"to\": 3256}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition to many offerings during the Olympics, Team USA gives access to seminars and therapy for the \\\"post-Olympic blues\\\" for athletes who are not planning to try and qualify for additional Olympics.\", \"from\": 3258, \"to\": 3461, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3309, \"end\": 3317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.99999999999